PuReST pupil detector + tracker
================================

Algorithm and original source: Thiago Santini, Wolfgang Fuhl,
Enkelejda Kasneci, University of Tübingen. Builds on PuRe (Santini et
al. 2018a) — see also `pupil_detectors/PuRe/LICENSE`.

Reference: Santini, T., Fuhl, W., Kasneci, E. (2018). "PuReST: Robust
pupil tracking for real-time pervasive eye tracking." *ETRA 2018*,
61:1-61:5. <https://doi.org/10.1145/3204493.3204578>

